data.description: Beautiful 4 sided Brick home on 4.23 acres! - So bring your horses if you like!  This well-maintained 4BR and 2 1/2 BA home is "move-in ready" -- Enter into the front door to an open floorplan and gorgeous hardwood flooring that runs throughout the house. The kitchen boasts beautiful quartz countertops, tile backsplash, refaced countertops, marble flooring, and stainless steel appliances. It opens up to a spacious breakfast area - along with a separate dining room for additional eating space. The owner's bedroom is spacious with private en-suite that includes, double vanity, separate shower, garden tub & walk-in closet. The bathrooms have well laid tile flooring.  The bonus room offers options of office space or additional guest bedroom. It has it own HVAC heating & air system.  The back porch/patio provides privacy and serenity as you overlook the fenced acreage and meditate over the Koi pond. There are various fruit trees along the property--- For added convenience, there is a nice sized storage building/barn, providing ample space for all of your storage needs. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this incredible home with its desirable features.  Schedule a showing today and make this your dream home!
